Usage: verifyIsolatedCut [-help] [-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}] [-error <integer>]
                         [-maxXY] [-report <string>] [-layer <string> ]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}     # specifies the area to check (box, optional)
-error <integer>        # Specifies the maximum number of errors to report
                        # (int, optional)
-layer <string>         # Specifies the cut layers to be checked.
                        # (string, optional)
-maxXY                  # Specifies the metric of checking cut distance
                        # (bool, optional)
-report <string>        # Specifies the report file that contains the
                        # violations informations (string, optional)